      <event start="T34" end="T35">prijaviš tiste osebe, </event>
      <event start="T35" end="T53-776">ko grejo. </event>
      <event start="T53-776" end="T36">Pa mora biti prav napisano. </event>
      <event start="T36" end="T56-595">Morajo biti vse črke prav. </event>
      <event start="T58-838" end="T37">Lahko eee z doplačilom, </event>
      <event start="T37" end="T38">mislim, da je deset evrov, </event>
      <event start="T38" end="T66-083">da zamenjaš eee naslov eee naslovnika karte. </event>
      <event start="T66-93" end="T39">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T39" end="T68-851">in pol s kartico plačaš. </event>
      <event start="T69-978" end="T72-147">Kartico imaš za plačati? </event>
      <event start="T72-636" end="T73-12">Bančno? </event>
      <event start="T73-508" end="T73-944">A imaš? </event>
      <event start="T75-105" end="T41">A no, </event>
      <event start="T41" end="T75-957">tisto imaš. </event>
      <event start="T75-957" end="T78-046">No, in pol ko plačaš ... </event>
      <event start="T78-046" end="T242">pol pa greš nazaj v aplikacijo </event>
      <event start="T242" end="T81-743">in narediš tisti check in. </event>
      <event start="T82-496" end="T44">Ne? </event>
      <event start="T44" end="T45">In tam ti piše pol, </event>
      <event start="T45" end="T121">ob koliki uri greš </event>
      <event start="T121" end="T46">in kdaj pristaneš. </event>
      <event start="T46" end="T88-976">In številko leta. </event>
      <event start="T88-976" end="T90-502">Pa za ... </event>
      <event start="T92-364" end="T50">Ja, no, </event>
