      <event start="T102-91" end="T105-010">Ma na, pa spet. </event>
      <event start="T105-010" end="T106-675">Pa tam rezervirajte tisto. </event>
      <event start="T107-182" end="T53">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T53" end="T112-081">samo moraš imeti eee tablico, registracijo </event>
      <event start="T112-081" end="T116-436">in pol tam daš od kdaj do kdaj, kateri datum in uro. </event>
      <event start="T117-061" end="T283">In pol tam pustiš </event>
