      <event start="T129-229" end="T130-94">No, </event>
      <event start="T130-94" end="T61">in ko boste prišle nazaj, </event>
      <event start="T61" end="T284">se usedeš v avto </event>
      <event start="T284" end="T134-639">in greš domov. </event>
      <event start="T137-504" end="T139-426">Saj boš počivala na letalu. </event>
