      <event start="T188" end="T857-814">imajo tudi majhna pakiranja. </event>
      <event start="T858-697" end="T859-368">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T859-368" end="T333">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T333" end="T861-279">menda po deset kil. </event>
      <event start="T865-811" end="T866-624">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T866-624" end="T190">Tako da ... </event>
      <event start="T190" end="T191">odvisno, koliko imaš prostora, no, </event>
      <event start="T191" end="T365">kakšne imaš tiste gredice, njivo, </event>
      <event start="T365" end="T871-881">ne vem. </event>
      <event start="T873-514" end="T367">Drugo pa ne vem, </event>
      <event start="T367" end="T192">kaj boš še sadila, </event>
      <event start="T192" end="T877-667">za bučke, tisto je pa še vse prezgodaj. </event>
      <event start="T878-754" end="T879-547">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T879-919" end="T193">Zdaj bi lahko to cvetačo, zelje bi lahko dala, </event>
      <event start="T193" end="T194">ko cvetača ti poleti, </event>
      <event start="T194" end="T335">če je prevroče, </event>
      <event start="T335" end="T885-507">noče delati. </event>
      <event start="T886-859" end="T887-822">Imajo. </event>
      <event start="T887-822" end="T892-498">Cvetača, zelje, eee brstični ohrovt, solate. </event>
      <event start="T892-498" end="T893-966">To sem videla jaz vse. </event>
      <event start="T893-966" end="T195">V vrtnariji, </event>
      <event start="T195" end="T895-705">pri Primožu. </event>
      <event start="T896-844" end="T899-311">Tako da to bi komot lahko sadila. </event>
      <event start="T900-695" end="T901-68">Ta prve cvet() ... </event>
      <event start="T902-49" end="T904-84">Ko ta prve cvetače so ta lepše, take ... </event>
      <event start="T905-870" end="T196">Ali pa pol jesenska, </event>
      <event start="T196" end="T908-109">poleti ti ne bo, </event>
      <event start="T908-109" end="T908-701">ne. </event>
      <event start="T909-001" end="T909-488">Pa </event>
      <event start="T909-616" end="T911-855">pa polno treba zalivati, ne. </event>
      <event start="T912-216" end="T197">Ja, seveda. </event>
      <event start="T197" end="T914-67">Cvetača rabi polno vode. </event>
      <event start="T915-022" end="T915-659">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T915-659" end="T337">Tudi, </event>
      <event start="T337" end="T368">ker je tu(), </event>
      <event start="T368" end="T338">pa zelje rabi, </event>
      <event start="T338" end="T918-371">moraš zalivati. </event>
      <event start="T918-752" end="T919-574">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T919-574" end="T923-271">Drugače pa lahko še korenček seješ, kakšno blitvo. </event>
      <event start="T924-346" end="T340">To, </event>
      <event start="T340" end="T926-602">redkvica. </event>
      <event start="T926-602" end="T199">Eee sem videla ima tudi r() sadike pora pa rdeče pese, </event>
      <event start="T199" end="T932-743">tako da imaš za naprej, ne. </event>
      <event start="T934-459" end="T935-590">Edino koren ... </event>
      <event start="T935-590" end="T369">tako, </event>
      <event start="T369" end="T938-404">edino korenček sadike niso v redu. </event>
      <event start="T938-861" end="T200">Ne, </event>
      <event start="T200" end="T370">ko pride korenček razvejan, </event>
      <event start="T370" end="T371">ni tak lep, raven, </event>
      <event start="T371" end="T944-074">kot bi moral biti. </event>
      <event start="T946-008" end="T341">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T341" end="T289">tako, ja, </event>
      <event start="T289" end="T201">pride kar nekaj. </event>
      <event start="T201" end="T373">Ko naleti na eno oviro, </event>
      <event start="T373" end="T952-448">rata vse se deformira tako. </event>
      <event start="T956-439" end="T957-422">Tudi, ja. </event>
      <event start="T957-422" end="T203">Ja, saj korenček rabi bolj tako ž() zemljo, </event>
      <event start="T203" end="T204">peščeno tako, ne, </event>
      <event start="T204" end="T963-2">da bo on, da bo lep. </event>
      <event start="T963-2" end="T965-491">Ko če je trdo, nima iti kam, </event>
      <event start="T965-491" end="T966-216">ne. </event>
      <event start="T966-216" end="T968-523">Ja, tako, tako, ja. </event>
      <event start="T969-11" end="T205">Tako. </event>
      <event start="T205" end="T206">Glih tako kot por, </event>
      <event start="T206" end="T972-55">ko ga moraš gor malo zagrebsti </event>
      <event start="T972-55" end="T973-775">eee da ima ... </event>
      <event start="T973-775" end="T207">tako, ja, </event>
      <event start="T207" end="T975-927">da ima čim več belega dela, ja. </event>
      <event start="T975-927" end="T342">Tistega uporabnega, </event>
      <event start="T342" end="T978-864">ja, tako. </event>
      <event start="T978-864" end="T208">Drugo pa ne vem. </event>
      <event start="T208" end="T209">Rukola bi bila zdaj, še bi lahko, </event>
      <event start="T209" end="T983-472">je dobra. </event>
      <event start="T986-524" end="T211">Lahko, ko daš loke </event>
      <event start="T211" end="T212">pa daš kopreno ono, </event>
      <event start="T212" end="T375">magari zdaj zimsko, </event>
      <event start="T375" end="T991-362">če jo imaš. </event>
      <event start="T992-66" end="T344">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T344" end="T993-332">je bolj gosta, ja, </event>
      <event start="T993-332" end="T996-483">letna koprena je pa bolj tanka. </event>
      <event start="T996-483" end="T1001-328">Ali pa daš najlon še, ne vem, pa čez kopreno ali nekaj. </event>
      <event start="T1002-45" end="T376">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T376" end="T213">ko skozi najlon pol zna sonce tudi z() to vse zapalit, </event>
      <event start="T213" end="T377">kadar fajn pali, </event>
      <event start="T377" end="T1009-463">zdaj če te ni tam, da nisi blizu. </event>
      <event start="T1009-463" end="T1011-278">Eee da bi to čez dan ... </event>
      <event start="T1011-278" end="T345">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T345" end="T1014-352">da lahko čez dan to kaj odgrneš, ne. </event>
      <event start="T1015-008" end="T1016-763">[glas] </event>
      <event start="T1016-763" end="T378">No, ko </event>
      <event start="T378" end="T214">ne vem, </event>
      <event start="T214" end="T379">v r() </event>
      <event start="T379" end="T215">tule mi, ko imamo v rastlinjaku, </event>
      <event start="T215" end="T216">so je noter pride savna. </event>
      <event start="T216" end="T380">Moraš čez dan odpreti, </event>
      <event start="T380" end="T1023-575">če ne, je vse skuhano. </event>
      <event start="T1023-575" end="T1025-231">Zdaj, k je bilo vro() tu je ... </event>
      <event start="T1026-746" end="T1027-531">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1027-531" end="T217">Edino če je bo napovedan kakšen bolj mraz, </event>
      <event start="T217" end="T381">ne vem, </event>
      <event start="T381" end="T1033-475">daš, če imaš, en kos najlona, ne. </event>
      <event start="T1033-475" end="T382">Pokriješ, </event>
      <event start="T382" end="T1035-701">tako da ... </event>
      <event start="T1036-387" end="T218">To je to, no. </event>
      <event start="T218" end="T219">Drugo pa ne vem. </event>
      <event start="T219" end="T1040-346">Kaj bi še kakšno drevje okrasno sadila? </event>
      <event start="T1042-498" end="T1043-376">Aha. </event>
      <event start="T1047-132" end="T1048-036">Malo ... </event>
      <event start="T1048-391" end="T1050-741">Okrasno ali češnjo ta pravo? </event>
      <event start="T1051-523" end="T290">Da bo sadež, </event>
      <event start="T290" end="T1052-914">aha. </event>
      <event start="T1052-914" end="T1053-437">No no. </event>
      <event start="T1054-576" end="T346">Aja, </event>
      <event start="T346" end="T222">tudi pri nas jo je, </event>
      <event start="T222" end="T1058-975">pa jo vsako leto samo ptiči pojejo. </event>
      <event start="T1060-405" end="T291">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T291" end="T1061-829">Ma ja, </event>
      <event start="T1061-829" end="T347">se da, ja, dati mrežo, </event>
      <event start="T347" end="T223">ma zrase visoko </event>
      <event start="T223" end="T1066-875">in pol ne moreš do njih, ne. </event>
      <event start="T1066-875" end="T224">In pol greš, </event>
      <event start="T224" end="T1069-947">se koplješ po kakšnih lojtrah. </event>
      <event start="T1069-947" end="T225">Ni vredno, </event>
      <event start="T225" end="T1072-362">ko lahko še padeš dol. </event>
      <event start="T1073-684" end="T1075-227">Mreže pa obstajajo, </event>
      <event start="T1075-227" end="T226">ja, da vržeš čez krošnjo, ne, </event>
      <event start="T226" end="T227">zdaj če pa rata preveliko drevo, </event>
      <event start="T227" end="T1082-506">je pa pol to vse skup veliko, visoko. </event>
      <event start="T1089-06" end="T1089-833">Ne, </event>
      <event start="T1089-833" end="T349">tisto se da kadar krompir, </event>
      <event start="T349" end="T1091-826">zato ko majo tisti gomolji ... </event>
      <event start="T1091-826" end="T1093-459">Ko krompir, ja. </event>
      <event start="T1093-459" end="T1096-471">Samo v jeseni moraš tisto skopati ven, </event>
      <event start="T1096-471" end="T1101-266">vse med gomolji očistiš eee tisto eee zemljo. </event>
      <event start="T1101-266" end="T350">In lepo pospraviš v eno klet </event>
      <event start="T350" end="T229">in spomladi spet sadiš </event>
      <event start="T229" end="T230">in pol daš še na pol, </event>
      <event start="T230" end="T1108-441">ker to rata gomolj pol še enkrat večji. </event>
      <event start="T1108-441" end="T1109-045">In se j() ... </event>
      <event start="T1109-665" end="T1110-248">Tako ja, </event>
      <event start="T1110-248" end="T231">se jih namno() </event>
      <event start="T231" end="T1112-954">imaš pol za z() naprej, ja. </event>
      <event start="T1112-954" end="T1114-96">Tako, ja. </event>
      <event start="T1119-706" end="T1120-77">Za rezano. </event>
      <event start="T1122-088" end="T1125-221">Pa cinije bi lahko sejala pa astre pa kakšne ... </event>
      <event start="T1125-678" end="T280">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T280" end="T233">kupiš seme. </event>
      <event start="T233" end="T384">Lahko kupiš sončnico, </event>
      <event start="T384" end="T234">jo daš kam. </event>
      <event start="T234" end="T385">Zdaj če je previsoka, </event>
      <event start="T385" end="T235">jo daš ob kakšen rob </event>
      <event start="T235" end="T1135-658">pa ti lepo, se lepo ona obrača proti soncu. </event>
      <event start="T1135-658" end="T236">In pol da imaš seme, </event>
      <event start="T236" end="T1139-661">tudi ptiči pol pojejo tisto seme. </event>
      <event start="T1139-661" end="T1141-921">Tako da ... to. </event>
      <event start="T1141-921" end="T386">Saj je polno tam, </event>
      <event start="T386" end="T237">tako, vse sort je rož, </event>
      <event start="T237" end="T263">samo pride noter v vrečki glih ene tri semena </event>
      <event start="T263" end="T1149-351">pa dostikrat tudi ven nič ne pride. </event>
      <event start="T1150-423" end="T1151-681">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T1151-681" end="T1152-432">tako slabo je, ja. </event>
      <event start="T1152-432" end="T1152-907">Pa ... </event>
      <event start="T1153-958" end="T238">Pa veš, kaj je tudi lepo? </event>
      <event start="T238" end="T1156-657">Kakšen ognjič. </event>
      <event start="T1156-657" end="T239">Da daš na njivo med [glas] malo sadik, </event>
      <event start="T239" end="T281">ga glih tako lahko poseješ, </event>
      <event start="T281" end="T1163-394">pa on se tudi pol kar vseje za naprej. </event>
      <event start="T1163-763" end="T282">Pa je lepo videti med zelenjavo </event>
      <event start="T282" end="T387">pa odganja neke škodljivce, </event>
      <event start="T387" end="T1167-669">ne vem. </event>
      <event start="T1167-669" end="T1168-578">Ali pa </event>
      <event start="T1168-578" end="T265">te eem </event>
      <event start="T265" end="T1171-491">ti turški nageljčki. </event>
      <event start="T1172-073" end="T1174-523">Tisto glih tako kupiš seme pa ... </event>
      <event start="T1174-523" end="T266">Eee turški, pa pobereš pol seme </event>
      <event start="T266" end="T267">pa imaš za naprej </event>
      <event start="T267" end="T1179-177">pa si poseješ. </event>
      <event start="T1179-177" end="T240">Pa glih tako odganja neke škodljivce, </event>
      <event start="T240" end="T1184-416">pa to pa lepo ... </event>
      <event start="T1184-416" end="T1188-294">Pa lepo je videti ob gredicah malo, da cveti med kakšno zelenjavo, </event>
      <event start="T1188-294" end="T1189-681">daš kakšen cvet, ja. </event>
      <event start="T1190-514" end="T1191-584">Ja, tako. </event>
      <event start="T1191-584" end="T1194-160">Da je lepo urejeno. </event>
    </tier>
